      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was just cleaning my ears with a qtip and i heard this weird loud pop in my left ear. now my left ear feels totally blocked and i honestly cant hear anything out of it at all. is this just like tinnitus or maybe just some wax stuck in there? it's kinda worrying but i dont want to go to the doctor if it's nothing",
